sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Open WebUI
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant A as ASR
    participant G as Guard
    participant R as Retrieval Stack
    participant L as Remote LLM
    participant T as TTS

    U->>UI: Voice query (WAV)
    UI->>O: chat request<br/>audio + text+audio

    rect rgb(255, 244, 244)
        Note over O: Normalize input
        O->>A: transcribe(audio)
        Note over A: Load on demand if idle
        A-->>O: text query
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        O->>G: classify input
        G-->>O: safe
    end

    rect rgb(240, 244, 255)
        O->>R: embed + search + rerank
        Note over R: Search econ_vn_news<br/>and econ_knowledge
        R-->>O: top context
    end

    rect rgb(255, 244, 255)
        O->>L: generate answer
        L-->>O: answer text
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        O->>G: classify output
        G-->>O: safe
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over O: Audio requested
        O->>T: synthesize(answer)
        T-->>O: WAV audio
    end

    O-->>UI: text + citations + audio
    UI-->>U: answer + playback
